  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text ">
    Research at IPO
  </h1>
</div>

    </div>
    
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    We carry out and commission research relating to intellectual property, patent applications, trade marks and copyright.
  </p>

      
